OL,5,G1955 Heartbeat
OL,6,     FMembers of the local constabulary
OL,7,     Fpatrol the town of Ashfordly and
OL,8,     Fthe nearby village of Aidensfield,
OL,9,     Fkeeping the peace whilst also
OL,10,     Fdealing with local loveable
OL,11,     Frogues.
OL,12,G2100 Out There
OL,13,     FNathan (Martin Clunes) is fighting
OL,14,     Fback against the dark urban menace
OL,15,     Fmaking their way into his
OL,16,     Fcommunity. Sometimes the familiar
OL,17,     Fworld can become a dangerous
OL,18,     Fplace.
