OL,5,G2200 Brianna: A Mother's Story
OL,6,     FWhen 16-year-old trans girl
OL,7,     FBrianna Ghey was murdered by
OL,8,     F15-year-olds Eddie Ratcliffe and
OL,9,     FScarlett Jenkinson, it sparked
OL,10,     Fgrief and anger across the UK and
OL,11,     Fthe world.
OL,12,G2300 Malpractice
OL,13,     FThis medical thriller combines a
OL,14,     Fsearing insight into the pressures
OL,15,     Fand politics of hospital life with
OL,16,     Fa gripping story about a damaged
OL,17,     Fdoctor caught up in a dangerous
OL,18,     Fconspiracy.
